message.body: I'm so sorry that I haven't been available to see you! I had two weddings out of town and I have worked/am working both colleges' reunion teen programs. Meaning zero weekends free in the last month to see my Martha! :( I might be in uptown for a few hours tomorrow afternoon. Any chance you're free?
I'm in new ulm for the weekend... Let me know when you're around again and I'll do the same
Sounds good! Say hi to your family for me!
